title: Misfit

description.plain:
On “Misfit,“ Juice WRLD raps about his desire to get money, women, and live a nonchalant lifestyle.

During the celebration of Juice WRLD Day on December 16, 2023, a fan asked Juice WRLD’s manager, Lil Bibby, about the first track on The Party Never Ends. In response, Lil Bibby revealed that this track would open the album.

The track ended up being second on the aforementioned album — which would serve as his final posthumous release — in November 2024, following the album’s titular intro track.
